  <lyrics>[V1]
 Juma jac'an Dios Awquejja,
 Nayajj jacañ munta.
 Jacañajjas Jumaruwa
 Wiñayatac churjjsma.
 
[C]
 Cusisisaw nayajj k'ochü
 Juma Dios Awatirír.
 Naya laycuw Jumajj jiwta,
 Calvario cruzana. (Bis)
 
[V2]
 Kollan Ajayump phokt'ita,
 Jumamp jacañatac.
 K'oma chuymay tucuyita,
 Jumar sirviñatac.
 
[V3]
 Ma uruw alajjpachanjja
 Jumampejj cusisl.
 Jan karjasisaw nayajja
 Jumarojj k'ochojja.
 
 </lyrics></song>